-- Deutsche Bahn to Raise Fares on Local, Regional Routes With New Schedule
-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 2010-10-13T09:26:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-13/deutsche-bahn-to-raise-fares-on-local-regional-routes-with-new-schedule.html
Deutsche Bahn AG said it will not
raise long-distance train fares when the new schedule takes
effect on Dec. 12, 2010. Fares on regional and local routes will
increase by an average of 1.9 percent, the company said in an e-
mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mike Gavin at 
 mgavin2@bloomberg.net  